01:45:41,556 --> 01:45:43,015
Je voulais le revoir.

1225
01:45:43,225 --> 01:45:44,138
Merci.

1226
01:45:44,476 --> 01:45:45,674
Mon cul !

1227
01:45:46,061 --> 01:45:49,726
